data.description: "Welcome to your dream townhouse in the heart of a secure gated community! This immaculate 3-bedroom, 2 full bath, and 2 half bath residence is the epitome of modern comfort and convenience.  Step into a newly renovated haven boasting brand new appliances and freshly installed carpet that exudes contemporary elegance. The main level welcomes you with the charm of refinished hardwood floors, adding a touch of sophistication to your living space.  Noteworthy features include an HVAC system installed in 2022 and a water heater replaced in 2021, providing peace of mind and efficiency for years to come.  Convenience meets lifestyle with the added advantage of being within walking distance to the metro station, making commuting a breeze and adding unparalleled ease to your daily routines.  Perfectly positioned in a gated community, this townhouse offers both security and a vibrant, welcoming atmosphere. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautifully maintained and conveniently located townhouse your new home sweet home!"
